regen.absent_element: option to extend searches to the internet via Google is not fully specified
regen.new_specification: The system shall provide an option on the dedicated search page to extend the search to the internet using a standard search engine such as Google, and display the results alongside the course management system results or in a separate section.

regen.absent_element: handling of no search results or empty search query
regen.new_specification: The system should handle cases where no search results are found or when an empty search query is submitted, and provide a corresponding message to the user.

regen.absent_element: handling of invalid or empty search queries
regen.new_specification: The system should handle and provide feedback for invalid or empty search queries, such as displaying an error message or suggesting related searches.
